00:09:27.539 --> 00:09:33.940
things that previously they heard from Jesus, but had not understood.

00:09:33.940 --> 00:09:38.539
God's spirit would also declare to them the things coming,

00:09:38.539 --> 00:09:44.299
including the bringing to light the significance of Jesus' death and resurrection.

00:09:44.340 --> 00:09:48.779
As these events were then yet future and were among the things

00:09:48.779 --> 00:09:53.620
